                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " The use of aggregation functions and joins can impact performance, especially if the underlying tables are large. Indexing on key columns like "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "InvoiceID",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
